# Place your Remotion video exports here.
# Render from sketch-fc-reel with:
#   npx remotion render src/index.ts SketchFC out/full.mp4
# Then trim and export individual clips:
#   s1-hook.mp4        (0–330 frames)
#   s2-wound.mp4       (330–690 frames)
#   s3-evidence.mp4    (690–1110 frames)
#   s4-system.mp4      (1110–1440 frames)
#   s5-scale.mp4       (1440–1710 frames)
#   s6-generation.mp4  (1710–1920 frames)
#   s7-closer.mp4      (1920–2130 frames)
# Note: these files are gitignored due to size.
